@node Main "BBBubbles - Documentation"

                            'BBBubbles' V1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'BBBubbles' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} where the goal is to burst as
many coloured bubbles on the game board as possible. But in order to
burst, two or more neighbouring bubbles have to be of the same size.
As you can guess, the more bubbles that blow up, particularly if they
are all of the same colour, the more points you get.

  Have fun!

